== 6...b5 ==
Black ends White's pressure on the c6 knight. 

[[/7. Bb3|'''7. Bb3''']] is necessary to save the bishop and the typical, automatic move. 

From time to time some bright spark will wheel out [[/7. d5|'''7. d5?!''']], the '''Richter variation''', which can entrap Black if they avoid trading knight for bishop. 

[[/7. Nxe5|'''7. Nxe5!?''']], the '''Friess attack''', can lead to a number of trades and an equal position. 7...Nxe5 8. dxe5 bxa4 9. Qd5 Rb8 10. Qxe4.

